{"tid":682140,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"丹尼爾5億天價片酬演占士邦","createTime":"2018-05-28T15:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T04:01:15.000Z","uid":1002,"like":105,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"6233412c75fc5407426d332b788e2036f36c0793","tid":682140,"uid":1002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:12:18.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】已主演了4集占士邦電影的英國演員丹尼爾格力(Daniel Craig)，在拍完《007：鬼影帝國》之後，曾表明自己不會再拍第5集。不過上年他上一個電視節目時，又推翻昨日的自己，話自己會第5度飾演占士邦，究竟什麼原因令他回心轉意呢？<br />\n<br />\n近日他唔嫁又嫁的理由終於揭盅了，其實原因好簡單，一切都係錢作怪！近日有消息指，他在新一集占士邦電影的片酬跳升至港幣5.2億的天價，比上一集《007：鬼影帝國》的3.8億高出大約三份一，除了主演電影，他更會兼任新一集電影的執行監製。至於新一集已確定由執導《迷幻列車》、《一百萬零一夜》的丹尼波爾(Danny Boyle)擔任導演，電影預計在今年年底開拍，並在2019年秋季上映。與第一代占士邦辛康納利(Sean Connery)一樣，今次丹尼爾會第5度飾演007，但仍未追平演足7次的羅渣摩亞(Roger Moore)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rW2v8Ah4FfAi13ZKMTGOrg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTUxMg--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/uAE7MAK0Cd.EFYbFY19AIA--~B/aD00MDA7dz01MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180528f121058.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FrW2v8Ah4FfAi13ZKMTGOrg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTUxMg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FuAE7MAK0Cd.EFYbFY19AIA--~B%2FaD00MDA7dz01MDA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180528f121058.jpg&h=cd96f10c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83c2f8ea1af2b886c3633f1307d81cc9e384b34a","tid":682140,"uid":157898,"like":30,"dislike":64,"score":-34,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:16:10.000Z","msg":"睇占士邦係想睇佢有幾風流同啲靚女主角<br />\n點知佢相反，係呀，佢有食過女，但食老野呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5042f1cac272f26dd9e0ef9171f716def576d748","tid":682140,"uid":113956,"like":141,"dislike":12,"score":129,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T15:17:06.000Z","msg":"以為哈利波特果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de3043ce9efeb21